question:
根据下面 $\mathrm{{pH}} = 1$ 介质中 $\mathrm{{Bi}}$ 的元素电势图:

$$
{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}\xrightarrow[]{{1.59}\mathrm{\;V}}{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }\xrightarrow[]{{0.32}\mathrm{\;V}}\mathrm{{Bi}}\xrightarrow[]{-{0.97}\mathrm{\;V}}{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}
$$

求电对 ${\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/\mathrm{{Bi}},{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3},{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}$ 的电极电势;

answer:
(1) ${E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/\mathrm{{Bi}}}\right) = \frac{{E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }}\right) \times 1 + {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }/\mathrm{{Bi}}}\right) \times 3}{1 + 3}$

$$
= \frac{{1.59}\mathrm{\;V} \times 1 + {0.32}\mathrm{\;V} \times 3}{4}
$$

$$
= {0.64}\mathrm{\;V}
$$

$$
{E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}}\right) = \frac{{E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }/\mathrm{{Bi}}}\right) \times 3 + {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {\mathrm{{Bi}}/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}}\right) \times 3}{3 + 3}
$$

$$
= \frac{{0.32}\mathrm{\;V} \times 3 + \left( {-{0.97}\mathrm{\;V}}\right) \times 3}{6}
$$

$$
= - {0.33}\mathrm{\;V}
$$

$$
{E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}}\right) = \frac{{E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Bi}}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}/{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }}\right) \times 1 + {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{BiO}}}^{ + }/\mathrm{{Bi}}}\right) \times 3 + {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {\mathrm{{Bi}}/{\mathrm{{BiH}}}_{3}}\right) \times 3}{1 + 3 + 3}
$$

$$
= \frac{{1.59}\mathrm{\;V} \times 1 + {0.32}\mathrm{\;V} \times 3 + \left( {-{0.97}\mathrm{\;V}}\right) \times 3}{7}
$$

$$
= - {0.051}\mathrm{\;V}
$$
